ure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;绿色背景上各种 Android 兼容智能手表的渲染&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-4No7X6CJt6AJt32aiT7v11oBio=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/71611007/226402_Android_Smartwatch_Buyers_Guide_WJoel.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 William Joel / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Wear OS 比它好得多过去是这样，所以现在是考虑智能手表的最佳时机。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23449363/best-android-smartwatches-wear-os&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23449363/best-android-smartwatches-wear-os" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23449363/best-android-smartwatches-wear-os</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-01T16:53:18-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-01T16:53:18-04:00</updated><title>苹果即将大力进军人工智能领域 iPad 销量反弹</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/A2Ex-WiRgLRRqMZzBpmeJXyui2Y=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73496630/247111_iPad_Pro_2024_AKrales_0891.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;VelR3S&quot;>;Apple 宣布了最新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/24155440/apple-ipad-pro-2024-review&quot;>;iPad Pro&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24155407/apple-ipad-air- review-2024&quot;>;iPad Air&lt;/a>; 平板电脑几个月前上市，经过几个季度的疲软销售后，新产品为该公司的 iPad 部门带来了显着的提振。结合服务和 Mac 的强劲表现，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2024/08/apple-reports-third-quarter-results/&quot;>;Apple 公布了季度收入&lt;/a>; 858 亿美元，比去年同期增长 5%。 iPhone 和可穿戴设备的收入相对持平，因为消费者正在等待新一波的产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;0E0KIR&quot;>;到 Apple 报告下一份财报时，该公司将推出 &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24210279/the-iphone-16-dummy&quot;>;iPhone 16&lt;/a>;、iPhone 16 Plus、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/8/1/24211070/now-its-the-iphone-16-pro&quot;>;iPhone 16 Pro&lt;/a>; 和 iPhone 16 Pro Max。除其他改进外，Pro 型号将配备稍大的显示屏，而标准 iPhone 将配备 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23889013/iphone-15-pro-action-button-programmability-possibility -powerful&quot;>;去年推出的操作按钮&lt;/a>;。那些...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211479/apple-q3-2024-earnings-ipad-services-mac-ai&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211479/apple-q3-2024-earnings-ipad-services-mac-ai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/1/24211479/apple-q3-2024-earnings-ipad-services-mac-ai</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-01T16:51:22-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-01T16:51:22-04:00</updated><title>十二南 AirFly Duo 机上耳塞适配器已降至最优惠价格</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;十二南方 AirFly Duo 插入飞机上的座椅靠背娱乐系统。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rxiKqU4dwjMju8GeUOk6NUtOAT8=/0x0:1219x813/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73496617/airflyduo.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;十二南方 AirFly Duo 已跌至 29.99 美元，创下历史新低。&lt;/em>; |图片：十二南&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;gpaZJn&quot;>;当您飞行时，降噪耳塞，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23365910/apple -airpods-pro-第二代-review&quot;>;AirPods Pro&lt;/a>;非常适合与外界隔绝，但它们有一个缺点：它们无法与飞机上的机上娱乐系统配合使用。幸运的是，像 &lt;strong>;Twelve South AirFly Duo&lt;/strong>; 这样的蓝牙发射器可以为您解决这个问题，现在，您可以在 &lt;a href= 上以 29.99 美元（优惠 15 美元）的历史低价购买一个。 “https://www.amazon.com/Twelve-South-Transmitter-Headphones-Airplanes/dp/B07Z13H4TP?tag=theverge02-20” rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>; 和&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cmNceon6HR7&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;51HT3I &quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;现